# S1-8 (2026-05-19) — Authenticode signing material. The .pfx and any password
# file MUST stay out of git. The .inf template + .csr are safe to commit (they
# only carry the public CSR; private key lives in the Windows cert store).
certs/*.pfx
certs/*.p12
certs/*.key
certs/*.password
certs/*-PRIVATE*
.env.production
.env.signing
